  "detailed_description": "Down Fast VR is the ultimate mountain biking game for virtual reality, an arcade racing experience like no other. With unique controls that make you feel like you're really riding the bike, you'll be able to take on four different locations with over 20 crazy downhill races.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ASYNC MULTIPLAYER RACE</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/6eb6a8dd6122c7d6a2698885b58b89f0.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/6eb6a8dd6122c7d6a2698885b58b89f0.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/6eb6a8dd6122c7d6a2698885b58b89f0.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Compete against players from all around the world in the asynchronous multiplayer mode, racing against their ghosts to beat the leaderboards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c505596a5fab4e1feab90480549088c0.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c505596a5fab4e1feab90480549088c0.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c505596a5fab4e1feab90480549088c0.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREERIDE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/a065b23cd2729acc20b3d6ff145eaa2d.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/a065b23cd2729acc20b3d6ff145eaa2d.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/a065b23cd2729acc20b3d6ff145eaa2d.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or, if you just want to explore and have some fun, check out the freeride mode where you can spectate the ghosts of other players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/b031f5978a9d8da9af335ccbefe645b3.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/b031f5978a9d8da9af335ccbefe645b3.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/b031f5978a9d8da9af335ccbefe645b3.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR BIKE</h2><br>Down Fast VR features three different bikes to choose from, each with its own unique style and handling.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DO STUNTS</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/70f528fa01bfea2872ac1e0cd425acab.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/70f528fa01bfea2872ac1e0cd425acab.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/70f528fa01bfea2872ac1e0cd425acab.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And when you're ready to show off your skills, pull off stunts like whips, 360s, frontflips, and backflips as you race to the finish line.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c7a208b2bf3c6671360fcbe29d23c290.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c7a208b2bf3c6671360fcbe29d23c290.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c7a208b2bf3c6671360fcbe29d23c290.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOIN THE COMMUNITY</h2><br>Down Fast VR is currently in Early Access, and as a solo developer, I'm always looking for player feedback to make the game even better. So if you want to help shape the future of Down Fast VR, come join our Discord community and let me know what you think!<br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "Down Fast VR is the ultimate mountain biking game for virtual reality, an arcade racing experience like no other. With unique controls that make you feel like you're really riding the bike, you'll be able to take on four different locations with over 20 crazy downhill races.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ASYNC MULTIPLAYER RACE</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/6eb6a8dd6122c7d6a2698885b58b89f0.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/6eb6a8dd6122c7d6a2698885b58b89f0.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/6eb6a8dd6122c7d6a2698885b58b89f0.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Compete against players from all around the world in the asynchronous multiplayer mode, racing against their ghosts to beat the leaderboards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c505596a5fab4e1feab90480549088c0.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c505596a5fab4e1feab90480549088c0.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c505596a5fab4e1feab90480549088c0.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREERIDE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/a065b23cd2729acc20b3d6ff145eaa2d.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/a065b23cd2729acc20b3d6ff145eaa2d.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/a065b23cd2729acc20b3d6ff145eaa2d.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or, if you just want to explore and have some fun, check out the freeride mode where you can spectate the ghosts of other players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/b031f5978a9d8da9af335ccbefe645b3.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/b031f5978a9d8da9af335ccbefe645b3.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/b031f5978a9d8da9af335ccbefe645b3.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR BIKE</h2><br>Down Fast VR features three different bikes to choose from, each with its own unique style and handling.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DO STUNTS</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/70f528fa01bfea2872ac1e0cd425acab.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/70f528fa01bfea2872ac1e0cd425acab.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/70f528fa01bfea2872ac1e0cd425acab.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And when you're ready to show off your skills, pull off stunts like whips, 360s, frontflips, and backflips as you race to the finish line.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c7a208b2bf3c6671360fcbe29d23c290.poster.avif?t=1675762501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c7a208b2bf3c6671360fcbe29d23c290.webm?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956860/extras/c7a208b2bf3c6671360fcbe29d23c290.mp4?t=1675762501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOIN THE COMMUNITY</h2><br>Down Fast VR is currently in Early Access, and as a solo developer, I'm always looking for player feedback to make the game even better. So if you want to help shape the future of Down Fast VR, come join our Discord community and let me know what you think!<br><br>",
